{"tid":415154,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"倫敦Uber不獲續牌　 或下月停運","createTime":"2017-09-26T17:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T07:20:16.000Z","uid":22675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"77fad64ffb6afb25950045686bdfae4ebdf2117c","tid":415154,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T17:56:08.000Z","msg":"2017年09月23日<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170923/large/17940328z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170923%2Flarge%2F17940328z.jpg&h=2b060b99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】電召汽車應用程式Uber又遭遇滑鐵盧！英國倫敦交通局宣佈，以「不適合」為理由拒絕Uber的續牌申請。Uber現有的牌照將於9月30日到期，但可以在21日內提出上訴，並且在等候上訴期間繼續營運。這意味Uber最快下月起在倫敦停運，對此消息，Uber拒絕發表評論。<br />\n<br />\n交通局斥缺乏企業責任<br />\n倫敦交通局在聲明中，批評Uber缺乏企業責任，導致潛在的公眾安全及保安問題。倫敦市長簡世德稱支持交通局的決定，認為「不需要為創新犧牲顧客安全和保安。」外媒指出，約有3到4萬名司機可能受影響。<br />\nUber新任行政總裁霍斯勞沙希上月透露，計劃在18至36個月內上市，即最快可在2019年首次公開發售（IPO）。Uber最新估值達680億美元（約5,300億港元），是全球估值最高的「獨角獸」初創公司。<br />\n早前，英國Uber宣佈，計劃於2025年前達到全車隊採用電動車的目標。今次不獲續牌，勢必對其計劃造成重大打擊。Uber去年虧損逾30億美元（約234億港元），今年首季再蝕逾7億美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170923/20161753\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170923%2F20161753&d=IdBFszoKiPkQB5KnNSRzXv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=9607a5e6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Ffinanceestate%2Fart%2F20170923%2F20161753&h=b8d42238\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/financeestate/art/20170923/20161753</a>"},{"pid":"df3b46d42c4ec290fd8c15bc1b9a69f6fb9a91f0","tid":415154,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T18:28:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b39fd4f5d5d06ebccbcdf03d244fececaf48409","tid":415154,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislik